column5: How can I help you?
what can I do to help with pager?
what can I do to help with tests?
what can I do to help with dockers?
yes sir!
what you want me to help on?
have you acknowledged the page?
please acknowledge the page at pagerduty.com or your app
ok, is there a JIRA to track this page?
I did not understand, have you created a JIRA for this page already?
please create a JIRA for this page
ok, do you know what is source of the page?
please refer to http://wikicentral.cisco.com/display/IPCBU/Indigo+On+Call+Support+FAQ+for+CES#IndigoOnCallSupportFAQforCES-IdentifyingSourceofPagerEvents on instructions to find source
do you need help from another team?
ok, great. good luck with your page! Please resolve the page when done.
I did not understand, do you need help with investigation?
do you know who can help?
i did not understand, can you engage SRE team to get help?
Engage the SRE team, by selecting I Need Help, and they'll get you hooked up to the right people: https://wiki.cisco.com/display/IPCBU/spark+call+Sre+Team
great, good luck with your page. Please resolve the page when done.
sorry, I do not know how to handle this!!!
hmm, do you have session ID of the failed test?
please refer to test report and find session ID from failed test log
can you find call trace and check where it failed?
Hi there!
Greetings from Dobby!
what kind of information you need?
Dobby can help with handling pagers, tests, auto attendant etc.!
what you looking for pager?
wiki for pager handling is @ http://cbabu-wiki.cisco.com:8080/display/HTAA/2AM+Document+CES+Auto+Attendant+Service
what you looking for tests?
wiki for automation tests is @ http://cbabu-wiki.cisco.com:8080/display/HTAA/Troubleshooting+CES+Sanity+Test+Failures
